{"tid":1490442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不可被仇恨支配，但絕不能忘記仇恨","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:52:26.000Z","uid":131691,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"475707266853ef3110cf2528036bd6f80a593ce2","tid":1490442,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"爲何不可被仇恨支配？因爲會自亂陣腳。<br />\n例：冇gear冇架罉，衝入狗總，被亂槍掃射<br />\n<br />\n爲何絕不能忘記仇恨？因爲會助紂爲虐。<br />\n例：雨傘後期，全港市民集體被政府洗腦，忘記抗爭爲咩，集體轉型嘉年華<br />\n<br />\n可謂報仇？不義嘅事發生咗，繼而冷靜咁實行仇恨，冷靜咁履行公義。<br />\n插爛休班警察隻眼之後點？唔會開live，唔會post連登，做完就得。<br />\n上門斬斷將軍澳藍絲手腳之後點？居民即時摧毀閉路電視片段，並表示冇目擊任何人。<br />\n<br />\n凡事冷靜，係因爲要報仇報得徹底，報得有效率。"},{"pid":"8728d6b334210664e52eb3c20611345653fb3c3b","tid":1490442,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"保持怒氣，理智釋放"},{"pid":"feaf9197e07a9ae85a4f7a5bd70b1955ce10320b","tid":1490442,"uid":208484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cM8LDQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM8LDQa.png&h=02707ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aa1tBEB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAa1tBEB.jpg&h=fee8aedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaY0sMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaY0sMh.jpg&h=2a9c28ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ce789aa7c628e60186ad33897de76b88bb5406d","tid":1490442,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">暗角</span>"},{"pid":"7573cf9631f8154a362afce1d17987aaf16d5db7","tid":1490442,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"香港人出名有效率，見到抗爭AI進化速度已經係鐵一般嘅證明，我相信此效率可以用喺報仇一事。"},{"pid":"24d198e14bf869a45e0ff8e4987a17d33ad28fab","tid":1490442,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislik